      "title": "Sri Lanka shares steady in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka shares were steady in the mid-day trade on Tuesday (23) after opening stronger, the Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index moved up 17.79 points or 0.20 percent to 9,105.38 at 1130 hours.",
        "The most liquid S&P SL20 slipped 9.67 points or 0.32 per cent to 2,998.03."
